1. Download & install Visual Studio 2017
2. Download & unpack openframeworks. Place it into KinectToolV2/of_v0.10.0_vs2017, 
3. Install openframeworks plugin for vs 2017 (https://openframeworks.cc/setup/vs/)
3. Donwload ofxKinectForWindows2 (https://github.com/elliotwoods/ofxKinectForWindows2), place into  KinectToolV2/of_v0.10.0_vs2017/addons
3. Download & install Kinect SDK 1.8, copy the SDK into KinectToolV2/KinectTool/KinectTool/lib/winKinect1/
4. Download & install Kinect SDK 2.0, copy the SDK into KinectToolV2/KinectTool/KinectTool/lib/winKinect2/